oals and beliefs.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAgriculture and politicsxHistoryxGermany (East). 0aAgriculture and politicszGermany (East)xHistory. 0aForest policyxHistoryxGermany (East). 0aForest policyzGermany (East)xHistory. 0aForests and forestryxPolitical aspectsxHistoryxGermany (East). 0aForests and forestryxPolitical aspectszGermany (East)xHistory. 0aHuman ecologyxHistoryxGermany (East)xGermany (East). 0aHuman ecologyzGermany (East)xHistory. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030013030040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300130300423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300130300/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles